highlights.text: “反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1560 days straight.
Anson Lo 盧瀚霆 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “Lemonade” is the highest at #3.
“藍剔未必是壞習慣” by Kiri T is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #47.
“耿耿於懷” by Juno Mak is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 89 spots at #84.
